    {
      "id": "d1713cfd_114f36bf",
      "file_path": "gui-editors/gui-editor-apex/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/gui/editors/apex/rest/handling/ApexEditorRestResource.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 223,
      "message": "I think application/yaml may be nicer in general since it documents the API. In this case, because this is a file download feature, it is more useful to keep it as text/plain. Setting \"application/yaml\" results in the browser not recognizing the data as a text file (likely due to application/yaml not being an official IANA media type).",
